Synopsis:
For generations, the people of the City of Ember have flourished in an 
amazing world of glittering lights underground. But Ember's once 
powerful generator is failing... and the great lamps that illuminate 
the city are starting to flicker.
Now, in a race against time, the citizens must search Ember for clues 
that will unlock the ancient mystery of the city's existence, and escape 
before the lights go out forever.
